jectory"},"96.63":{"start":"96.63","dur":"1.96","text":"that it had never, ever seen"},"98.71":{"start":"98.71","dur":"2.08","text":"before. Now, this is a"},"100.79":{"start":"100.79","dur":"1.76","text":"really happy story. It&#39;s a fundamentally"},"102.55":{"start":"102.55","dur":"2.02","text":"happy story. There were some challenges"},"104.57":{"start":"104.57","dur":"1.81","text":"that came up along the way. These"},"106.38":{"start":"106.38","dur":"2.09","text":"big shifts are never accomplished"},"108.95":{"start":"108.95","dur":"1.3","text":"without some challenges"},"110.57":{"start":"110.57","dur":"1.43","text":"In this country we had"},"112.07":{"start":"112.07","dur":"1.58","text":"terrible smog, killer"},"113.80":{"start":"113.8","dur":"1.45","text":"smog for a while"},"115.47":{"start":"115.47","dur":"1.44","text":"We had terrible exploitation"},"116.91":{"start":"116.91","dur":"1.97","text":"of child labour. We don&#39;t have"},"118.94":{"start":"118.94","dur":"1.47","text":"those things anymore here. We"},"120.41":{"start":"120.41","dur":"1.59","text":"made choices as a people"},"122.34":{"start":"122.34","dur":"1.44","text":"to deal with the problems"},"123.96":{"start":"123.96","dur":"1.35","text":"There is no more child labour"},"125.34":{"start":"125.34","dur":"1.87","text":"in Britain, and the skies here"},"127.25":{"start":"127.25","dur":"1.38","text":"are cleaner than they&#39;ve been since"},"128.63":{"start":"128.63","dur":"1.69","text":"at least the 1500s"},"130.91":{"start":"130.91","dur":"1.38","text":"So challenges come up. What"},"132.32":{"start":"132.32","dur":"1.72","text":"astonishes me is how"},"134.04":{"start":"134.04","dur":"1.63","text":"good a job we do of dealing"},"135.67":{"start":"135.67","dur":"2.55","text":"with them. Now, I drew these"},"138.22":{"start":"138.22","dur":"1.32","text":"pictures to tell you a story about"},"139.54":{"start":"139.54","dur":"1.85","text":"what&#39;s going on right now"},"141.50":{"start":"141.5","dur":"1.72","text":"because I honestly believe"},"143.22":{"start":"143.22","dur":"1.25","text":"and the reason we titled our"},"144.47":{"start":"144.47","dur":"1.57","text":"book The Second Machine Age"},"146.38":{"start":"146.38","dur":"1.47","text":"is, that all of us have the really"},"147.85":{"start":"147.85","dur":"1.17","text":"good fortune to be here"},"149.27":{"start":"149.27","dur":"1.73","text":"at a time when we&#39;re seeing"},"151.37":{"start":"151.37","dur":"1.71","text":"the next huge leap"},"153.14":{"start":"153.14","dur":"1.65","text":"forward with technology"},"155.16":{"start":"155.16","dur":"1.57","text":"the next amazing acceleration"},"156.73":{"start":"156.73","dur":"1.28","text":"in technological progress"},"158.19":{"start":"158.19","dur":"1.36","text":"and it&#39;s coming as a result"},"159.55":{"start":"159.55","dur":"1.7","text":"of all these things we&#39;re doing"},"161.49":{"start":"161.49","dur":"1.6","text":"with our new digital tools"},"163.18":{"start":"163.18","dur":"1.73","text":"with software and hardware"},"164.91":{"start":"164.91","dur":"1.31","text":"and networks and robots and"},"166.22":{"start":"166.22","dur":"1.29","text":"artificial intelligence and"},"167.51":{"start":"167.51","dur":"1.57","text":"mobile. All this grab"},"169.14":{"start":"169.14","dur":"1.41","text":"bag of stuff that we have"},"171.20":{"start":"171.2","dur":"1.71","text":"honestly I believe is really changing"},"172.91":{"start":"172.91","dur":"1.5","text":"the trajectory of human history"},"174.41":{"start":"174.41","dur":"0.32","text":"again."}}